663
00:26:04.470 --> 00:26:05.590
oh Circe,

664
00:26:05.830 --> 00:26:07.909
cual varón que fuese razonable

665
00:26:07.910 --> 00:26:10.470
osara probar la comida y la bebida antes

666
00:26:10.470 --> 00:26:13.270
